3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses an automated method for brain tissue segmentation, which is a common application of AI in medical imaging.
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper involves the use of neural networks for brain tissue segmentation, which falls under the scope of this sub-category.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with the analysis of MRI scans, which can be considered as a form of multimedia data.
